Class PlottableData

java.lang.Object
ib.grapher.PlottableData
public class PlottableData extends Object
A class which stores a single set of plottable data.

      public void save()
      Saves this plottable data set to the output file, overwriting an existing entry for the set. If this plottable data has not yet been added, FileDataManager.encodeForInsertion(PlottableData) should be used instead.
